  "texts": [
    "The opaque nature of decision-making in many AI systems remains a central concern, especially in healthcare.",
    "Without interpretability, clinicians may struggle to trust or validate model outputs (Amann et al., 2020).",
    "The emerging field of eXplainable AI (XAI) seeks to resolve this issue by designing more transparent systems (Longo et al., 2024; Luo & Specia, 2024).",
    "Attempts to figure out how NN encode articulatory features of speech as compared to the neural representations are being made now (Beguš et al., 2023).",
    "Even accurate predictions must be approached cautiously."
  ],
